race.comment: HEDONIST (5) was a dominant winner at Warrnambool when last seen, leading throughout and putting five lengths on his nearest rival. That was a bit of a spike performance but a repeat goes a long way to winning. ILLYIVY (10) hasn't quite fired in two runs back but will be fitter for them and her best is good enough with Lane going aboard. TWO WOLVES (12) won well at Sandown Lakeside last time and can measure up. TAZIMA (6) was consistent last time in work and has been readied with two trials so looking for a good return.
